Sales Excellence Trainer - Bulgari - Dubai
29 Apr 2014 11:49 AM - UAE
Job Description: Description: A
Accountabilities Deployment of the Shopping@Bulgari training to store Staff, constantly enhancing selling skills, and development of the future additional modulesCoaching to the Store Managers, Retail Managers, staff on selling skills aspectsWork with store managers/teams on KPIs and prepare action plans related to their resultsDevelop and follow up action plans related to Mystery Shopping initiatives in coordination with CMDs, Retail Managers, Store ManagersCoaching on the importance of the Visual Merchandising, competition knowledge and brand/product stories to maximize sales performanceOrganize and perform follow up sessions at store levelEnsure proper deployment of the training related materialsOrganize and perform follow up sessions for openings/renovation or headcount rotation/turnoverCoordination with HR Department (Development and Training) for action plans related to Store Managers and staff on soft skills training Professional Competencies Relevant experience in training/sales (5 years) preferably for luxury business.Selling SkillsCoaching techniqueCommunication SkillsObservation, Feedback, Training on the jobTraining MethodologiesNegotiationKnowledge of the relevant market (competitors, luxury business)Fluent in English Personal Competencies Interpersonal sensitivityCustomer orientationOwnershipImpactNegotiationBusiness awarenessNetworkingSelf development Job Ad
